        <div class="row justify-content-center features">
          <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-5 col-lg-4 item">
            <div data-aos="fade-down" data-aos-duration="700" class="box">
              <i class="fa fa-notes-medical icon"></i>
              <h3 class="name">Maintain Health Record</h3>
              <p class="description">
                Medi Doc also gives you one centralized hub to manage all your
                patient’s medical data and gives you visibility into
                longitudinal medical histories .It can be done by retrieving the
                user’s medical data or either manually by the user .
              </p>
              <a class="learn-more" href="#">Learn more »</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-5 col-lg-4 item">
            <div data-aos="fade-down" data-aos-duration="700" class="box">
              <i class="fa fa-stethoscope icon"></i>
              <h3 class="name">Disease Diagnosis</h3>
              <p class="description">
                Medi Doc is a automatic disease detection application targeted
                by the symptoms diagnosis, that enables them to instantly
                diagnose diseases such as flu, cold, hypertension, skin disease,
                etc. through the symptoms provided by the user.
              </p>
              <a class="learn-more" href="#">Learn more »</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-5 col-lg-4 item">
            <div data-aos="fade-down" data-aos-duration="700" class="box">
              <i class="fa fa-calendar-check icon"></i>
              <h3 class="name">Search and Book an Appointment</h3>
              <p class="description">
                It also features a Search Engine and Online Appointment Booking
                platform Search Doctors, Hospitals, Diagnostic Centers and
                Pharmacies Search by Name, Specialty and Location Book an
                appointment online
              </p>
              <a class="learn-more" href="#">Learn more »</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-5 col-lg-4 item">
            <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="700" class="box">
              <i class="fa fa-robot icon"></i>
              <h3 class="name">Medical Consultant Bot</h3>
              <p class="description">
                A Smart Medical assistant bot that could solve the queries of
                the user by directly interacting with them.
              </p>
              <a class="learn-more" href="#">Learn more »</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-5 col-lg-4 item">
            <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="700" class="box">
              <i class="fa fa-hand-holding-medical icon"></i>
              <h3 class="name">Predict Medical Condition</h3>
              <p class="description">
                Use full medical histories to provide personalized care to
                patients faster and predict the present condition of the user.
              </p>
              <a class="learn-more" href="#">Learn more »</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-5 col-lg-4 item">
            <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="700" class="box">
              <i class="fa fa-file-medical-alt icon"></i>
              <h3 class="name">Appointment History</h3>
              <p class="description">
                You can view all your appointments in this section and also use
                the email and the appoitment reciept as a proof.
              </p>
              <a class="learn-more" href="#">Learn more »</a>
